rows.label: qst701509_msg0003
rows.name:
It's been too long, Teo. You look older...
as do I.

rows.label: qst701509_msg0004
rows.name:
Well, I never. Well, I never!
What's the occasion?

rows.label: qst701509_msg0005
rows.name:
Have you finished your best work?
I've been waiting to see that.

rows.label: qst701509_msg0006
rows.name:
You've been waiting? Even though
I didn't write to you even once?

rows.label: qst701509_msg0007
rows.name:
You've never been waiting all this time.
Heh heh! I know when you're pulling
my leg.

rows.label: qst701509_msg0008
rows.name:
Ho ho. You've not changed either.
You still laugh when you're
embarrassed.
